This tool implements the EDPB "Template for personal data breach notification"
v1.0 (adopted 8 June 2026, public consultation until 5 August 2026). It is a
technical reference for interoperability and preparation; it is NOT an official
submission channel and must not be used for live notifications to a supervisory
authority until the authorities implement the template.
